 Âó®ÔºåÊàëÊòØ Zakk„ÄÇ‰ΩèÂú®Êæ≥Ê¥≤Èõ™Ê¢®ÁöÑÂïÜÁßëÂ≠∏ÁîüÔºåÊúÉÁî®ÈõôË™ûÂØ´ Gentoo / Linux Á≠ÜË®ò„ÄÅË®≠Ë®àÂ∞èÂØ¶È©ó„ÄÅÁêÜË≤°ÂøÉÂæóÔºå‰ª•ÂèäÂíå Paper ÈÇÑÊúâÂÖ©ÈöªÂ§©Á´∫Èº†ÁöÑÁîüÊ¥ªË®ò‰∫ã„ÄÇ ÊàëÂíå Paper Âæû 2025 Âπ¥ 8 Êúà 7 Êó• ÈñãÂßãÈÅ†Ë∑ùÔºàÊæ≥Ê¥≤ÔºçÂè∞ÁÅ£ÔºâÔºåÊàëÂÄëÈÉΩÊòØÊ≥õÊÄßÊàÄ ü©∑üíõü©µÔºåÊúÉ‰∏ÄËµ∑ÂàÜ‰∫´ÊØèÊó•Ë°åÁ®ã„ÄÅÈü≥Ê®ÇÊ≠åÂñÆ„ÄÅË®≠Ë®àÈùàÊÑüÔºå‰πüÂú® ÊôÇÈñìËª∏ ‰∏äË®òÈåÑÁõ∏ËôïÁöÑÂ§©Êï∏„ÄÇ ÊëòË¶Å # üìç Èõ™Ê¢®ÁîüÊ¥ªÔºåÊôÇÂçÄÂú® AEST / AEDTÔºå‰∏ª‰øÆÂïÜÊ•≠„ÄÇ üß† ËààË∂£ÔºöGentoo„ÄÅLinux„ÄÅÊ∞õÂúçÈü≥Ê®Ç„ÄÅË®≠Ë®àÁ≥ªÁµ±„ÄÅÁêÜË≤°ËàáÊï¥ÁêÜÁîüÊ¥ª„ÄÇ üéÆ Êó•Â∏∏Â®õÊ®ÇÔºöÂíå Paper ‰∏ÄËµ∑Ë™ûÈü≥„ÄÅÁï´Áï´„ÄÅÊâìÈõªÂãï„ÄÅÁ†îÁ©∂Ë®≠ÂÇô„ÄÇ üêπ ÂÆ∂Ë£°ÊàêÂì°ÔºöPotato Ëàá Hash Brown ÂÖ©Èöª Teddy Â§©Á´∫Èº†„ÄÇ ÊàëÂíå Paper # ÊàëÂÄëÊòØÂú® Ceylan ÁöÑ Discord Ë™çË≠òÔºå‰∏ÄÈñãÂßãÂè™ÊòØËÅäÂ§©ÂàÜ‰∫´ÁîüÊ¥ªÔºåÂæå‰æÜËÆäÊàêÊØèÂ§©‰∫íÁõ∏Èô™‰º¥„ÄÅÂêåÊ≠•ÂΩºÊ≠§Êó•Á®ãÁöÑÈªòÂ•ë‰ºô‰º¥„ÄÇÊàëÂÄëÊØèÈöîÂπæÂÄãÊúàÊúÉÂÆâÊéíË¶ãÈù¢ÔºåPaper ÁõÆÂâçÂú®Âè∞ÁÅ£ÂøµÈ´ò‰∏âÔºå‰πãÂæåÊúÉ‰æÜÊæ≥Ê¥≤ÂøµÊõ∏„ÄÇÊÉ≥ÁúãÊàëÂÄëÁöÑÊó•Â∏∏ÂèØ‰ª•ËøΩËπ§ Paper ÁöÑ IGÔºö @abyss_74.50 Ôºå‰πüÂèØ‰ª•Âà∞ ÊôÇÈñìËª∏ ÁúãÂØ¶ÈöõÂ§©Êï∏„ÄÇ
Â§©Á´∫Èº† # Hash BrownÔºà2025/06/24Ôºâ # Ê∑∫Ê£ïËâ≤ TeddyÔºåÊ¥ªÂäõÊªøÈªûÔºåÊúÄÊÑõÂú®Á±†Â≠êË£°Ë°ùÂà∫„ÄÅÊê¨ÁßªÂ∞èÂ±ã„ÄÇ ÁúãÂà∞‰∫∫ÊàñÂÜ∞ÁÆ±Â∞±ÊúÉÁî®‰∏≠ÊñáÁöÑ„Äå515151„ÄçËÅ≤Èü≥Ë®éÈ£ü„ÄÇ ÊúÄÊÑõÔºöÁ¥ÖÔºèÁ∂†ÁîúÊ§í„ÄÅÁéâÁ±≥È¨ö„ÄÅÁ¥ÖËòøËîî„ÄÇ Êõ¥Â§öÁÖßÁâáÊúÉÊîæÂú® Instagram @zakk.au„ÄÇ PotatoÔºà2025/07/27Ôºâ # Ê∑±Ê£ïËâ≤ TeddyÔºåË∂ÖÊÑõÂêÉÂèàÂæàÂãáÊï¢ÔºåÂÅ∂ÁàæÈÇäÂêÉÈÇä‰æø‰æø„ÄÇ ÂæàÊúÉÊääËá™Â∑±ÂüãÂú®ÁâßËçâË£°Áù°Ë¶∫ÔºåÈÜí‰æÜÁπºÁ∫åÂêÉ„ÄÇ ÊúÄÊÑõÔºöÁîúÊ§í„ÄÅÁéâÁ±≥È¨ö„ÄÅÁ¥ÖËòøËîî„ÄÇ ÊôÇÈñìËª∏ ‰∏äÂèØ‰ª•ÁúãÂà∞Â•πÁöÑÂ§©Êï∏Ôºå‰πüÊúÉÂú® IG ÈôêÂãïÂá∫Áèæ„ÄÇ ‰∏ªË¶ÅË®≠ÂÇô # Ê°åÊ©ü # ASUS ROG STRIX X670E-A GAMING WIFI ‰∏ªÊ©üÊùø AMD Ryzen 9 7950X3DÔºà16 Ê†∏ / 32 Âü∑Ë°åÁ∑íÔºâ NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4080 SUPER È°ØÁ§∫Âç° 64 GB DDR5 6400 MHz Ë®òÊÜ∂È´î Aussie Telecom 1000/50 Mbps ÂÖâÁ∫ñÔºåWi-Fi 7 ‰∏âÈ†ªË∑ØÁî±Âô® Samsung Odyssey G9 49 ÂêãÔºà5120√ó1440ÔºåHDMI 2.1Ôºâ Windows 11 Pro Ëàá Gentoo LinuxÔºàKDE PlasmaÔºâÈõôÁ≥ªÁµ± Á≠ÜÈõª # Apple MacBook Air M2Ôºà16 GB / 512 GBÔºâ ASUS ROG Zephyrus G16 AirÔºàIntel Core Ultra 9 185H„ÄÅ32 GB LPDDR5X„ÄÅ1 TB SSD„ÄÅRTX 4060Ôºâ ÊâãÊ©üÔºàÁèæÂΩπËàáÈô∏Á∫åÈÄÅÁµ¶ÂÆ∂‰∫∫ÁöÑÊ©üÂûãÔºâ # Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 7„ÄÅSamsung Galaxy S25 Ultra„ÄÅGoogle Pixel 7 Pro iPhone 17 Pro„ÄÅiPhone 17 Pro Max„ÄÅiPhone 16 Pro iPhone 15 Pro„ÄÅiPhone 15 Pro Max„ÄÅiPhone 14 Pro„ÄÅiPhone 14 ËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºè # InstagramÔºö @zakk.au GitHubÔºöZakkaus XÔºö @zakkauu EmailÔºöadmin@zakk.au border:1px solid #34363a !important; } /* ÁßªÈô§ËàäË£ùÈ£æ */ .about-page .about-hero::before, .about-page .about-hero::after{ content:none !important; }
/* Âº∑Ë™øË©ûÔºöÊîπÁî®ÂçäÈÄèÊòéÂ∫ïÁ∑ö + ‰∏ªËâ≤ÊñáÂ≠óÔºà‰∏çÂÜçËÜ†ÂõäÔºâ */ .about-page .about-hero strong{ background: linear-gradient(to top,rgba(225,48,108,.32),rgba(225,48,108,0) 65%) !important; color:var(&ndash;about-accent) !important; padding:0 .2rem 0 .2rem !important; margin:0 .15rem 0 0 !important; border-radius:4px !important; font-weight:600; line-height:1.25; display:inline-block; letter-spacing:.25px; } body.dark .about-page .about-hero strong{ background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(225,48,108,.45),rgba(225,48,108,0) 65%) !important; color:#ff8fb7 !important; }
/* Hero ÊÆµËêΩÈñìË∑ùÂæÆË™ø */ .about-page .about-hero p{margin:.55rem 0 !important;} .about-page .about-hero p:first-child{margin-top:0 !important;} .about-page .about-hero p:last-child{margin-bottom:.2rem !important;}
/* Ê®ôÈ°åÔºöÊõ¥Á¥∞Á∑ªÂ∑¶Á∑öÔºåÂéªÈô§Â§öÈ§ò padding */ .about-page h3{ padding:0 0 .3rem .75rem !important; margin:1.9rem 0 .55rem !important; font-size:.98rem !important; line-height:1.25; font-weight:600; position:relative; background:linear-gradient(to right,rgba(225,48,108,.10),rgba(225,48,108,0) 72%) !important; border-radius:6px !important; } .about-page h3::before{ width:2px !important; background:var(&ndash;about-accent) !important; bottom:.3rem !important; } .about-page h3::after{ content:&quot;&quot;; position:absolute; left:.75rem; bottom:0; height:2px; width:64px; background:var(&ndash;about-accent); border-radius:2px; opacity:.78; } body.dark .about-page h3, body.dark .about-page h3::after{ background:linear-gradient(to right,rgba(225,48,108,.22),rgba(225,48,108,0) 72%) !important; opacity:.9; }
/* Á¨¨‰∏ÄÂÄãÊ®ôÈ°åÔºàÁ∑äÊé• heroÔºâÂÜçÁï•Á∏Æ */ .about-page .about-hero + h3{ margin-top:1.35rem !important; }
/* ÂàóË°® */ .about-page h3 + ul { list-style: none; margin:.15rem 0 .2rem !important; padding: 0; } .about-page h3 + ul li { position: relative; padding:.4rem 0 .4rem 1.15rem !important; font-size: .9rem; } .about-page h3 + ul li::before { content: &ldquo;&rdquo;; position: absolute; left: 0; top: .98rem; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(&ndash;about-accent); opacity: .55; } body.dark .about-page h3 + ul li::before { opacity: .75; }
/* ÈÄ£ÁµêÔºà‰∏ÄËà¨Ôºâ */ .about-page a[href^=&ldquo;http&rdquo;], .about-page a[href^=&ldquo;mailto:&rdquo;] { color: var(&ndash;about-accent); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: color .18s; } .about-page a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
/* ËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºè Pills */ .about-page .about-contacts { list-style: none; margin: .55rem 0 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .55rem .65rem; } .about-page .about-contacts li { margin: 0; padding: 0; } .about-page .about-contacts li::before { display: none; } .about-page .about-contacts a { background: var(&ndash;about-pill-bg-light); padding: .48rem .85rem .5rem; font-size: .7rem; letter-spacing: .45px; line-height: 1; border-radius: 9px; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; color: var(&ndash;about-accent); transition: background .22s, color .22s; } body.dark .about-page .about-contacts a { background: var(&ndash;about-pill-bg-dark); color: #ff8fb7; } .about-page .about-contacts a:hover { background: var(&ndash;about-accent); color: #fff; }
/* === Ë¶ÜËìãÔºöËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºèÊîπÁÇ∫ÂûÇÁõ¥ÂàóË°®ÔºåÁµ±‰∏ÄÈ¢®Ê†º === */ .about-page .about-contacts{ display:block !important; flex-wrap:nowrap !important; gap:0 !important; margin:.2rem 0 0 !important; padding:0 !important; list-style:none; } .about-page .about-contacts li{ display:block !important; position:relative; margin:0 0 .45rem !important; padding:.42rem 0 .42rem 1.15rem !important; background:transparent !important; } .about-page .about-contacts li:last-child{margin-bottom:0 !important;} .about-page .about-contacts li::before{ content:&quot;&quot;; position:absolute; left:0;top:.95rem; width:6px;height:6px; background:var(&ndash;about-accent); border-radius:50%; opacity:.55; } body.dark .about-page .about-contacts li::before{opacity:.75;} .about-page .about-contacts a{ background:rgba(225,48,108,.14) !important; padding:.28rem .55rem .32rem !important; border-radius:6px !important; font-size:.72rem !important; letter-spacing:.3px; line-height:1; display:inline-block; text-decoration:none; color:var(&ndash;about-accent); transition:background .2s,color .2s; } body.dark .about-page .about-contacts a{ background:rgba(225,48,108,.30) !important; color:#ff8fb7 !important; } .about-page .about-contacts a:hover{ background:var(&ndash;about-accent) !important; color:#fff !important; }
/* È†ÅÈù¢È†ÇÈÉ®Ëàá Hero ÈñìË∑ùÔºàËÆìÊ®ôÈ°å/Êó•ÊúüËàáÂÖßÂÆπÊãâÈñãÔºâ */ .about-page{ padding-top:1.2rem !important; }
/* ÈÄöÁî®ÊÆµËêΩÊ®ôÈ°åÈñìË∑ùÔºàÁ∏ÆÁü≠ÊÆµËêΩÈñìÁ©∫ÁôΩÔºâ */ .about-page h3{ margin:1.9rem 0 .55rem !important; }
/* ÂàóË°®Ëàá‰∏ã‰∏ÄÊ®ôÈ°å‰πãÈñìË∑ùÈõ¢Êõ¥Á∑äÊπä */ .about-page h3 + ul{ margin:.15rem 0 .2rem !important; } .about-page h3 + ul li{ padding:.4rem 0 .4rem 1.15rem !important; }
/* ËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºèÂçÄÂ°äÈ†ÇÈÉ®ÂÜçÊî∂ÊñÇ */ .about-page h3:has(+ .about-contacts){ margin-top:1.6rem !important; } .about-page .about-contacts{ margin:.2rem 0 0 !important; }
/* === Áµ±‰∏ÄÔºöË®≠ÂÇôËàáËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºèÂàóË°®È¢®Ê†ºË¶ÜÂØ´ (ÈõôË™ûÂêåÊ≠•‰ΩøÁî®) === / .about-page{ &ndash;about-list-font:.9rem; &ndash;about-list-gap:.42rem; &ndash;about-bullet-size:6px; &ndash;about-link-pill:0; / Ëã•ÈúÄ pill Ê®£ÂºèÊîπÊàê 1 */ }
/* ÊâÄÊúâ h3 ÂæåÁöÑÂàóË°®ËàáËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºèÁµ±‰∏ÄÂü∫Â∫ï */ .about-page h3 + ul, .about-page .about-contacts{ list-style:none !important; margin:.35rem 0 .3rem !important; padding:0 !important; display:block !important; }
.about-page h3 + ul li, .about-page .about-contacts li{ position:relative; padding:var(&ndash;about-list-gap) 0 var(&ndash;about-list-gap) 1.1rem !important; margin:0 !important; font-size:var(&ndash;about-list-font); line-height:1.45; }
.about-page h3 + ul li::before, .about-page .about-contacts li::before{ content:&quot;&quot;; position:absolute; left:0;top:.95rem; width:var(&ndash;about-bullet-size); height:var(&ndash;about-bullet-size); background:var(&ndash;about-accent); border-radius:50%; opacity:.55; } body.dark .about-page h3 + ul li::before, body.dark .about-page .about-contacts li::before{ opacity:.75; }
/* ÈÄ£ÁµêÊ®ôÊ∫ñÂåñ */ .about-page .about-contacts a, .about-page h3 + ul li a{ color:var(&ndash;about-accent); font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; position:relative; padding:.05rem .1rem; border-radius:4px; transition:color .18s,background-color .18s; }
/* Èùû pill Ê®°ÂºèÔºàÈ†êË®≠Ôºâ‰∏ã hover Âè™ÊîπÈ°èËâ≤ÊàñËºïÂ∫ïËâ≤ */ .about-page .about-contacts a:hover, .about-page h3 + ul li a:hover{ text-decoration:underline; }
/* ÂèØÈÅ∏ pill Ê®°ÂºèÔºöÂ∞á &ndash;about-link-pill Ë®≠ 1 ÂïüÁî® / .about-page[style=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] .about-contacts a, .about-page[style*=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] h3 + ul li a{ padding:.38rem .65rem; background:rgba(225,48,108,.12); text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-size:.68rem; letter-spacing:.4px; line-height:1; } body.dark .about-page[style*=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] .about-contacts a, body.dark .about-page[style*=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] h3 + ul li a{ background:rgba(225,48,108,.28); color:#ff8fb7; } .about-page[style*=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] .about-contacts a:hover, .about-page[style*=&quot;&ndash;about-link-pill:1&quot;] h3 + ul li a:hover{ background:var(&ndash;about-accent); color:#fff; text-decoration:none; }
/* ÁßªÈô§ËàäËÅØÁµ°ÊñπÂºèË¶ÜÂØ´ÊÆòÁïôÔºàËã•‰πãÂâçÂ≠òÂú®Ôºâ */ .about-page .about-contacts li::after{content:none!important;}
/* Ë°åÂãïË£ùÁΩÆÂæÆË™ø */ @media (max-width:640px){ .about-page h3 + ul li, .about-page .about-contacts li{ padding:.38rem 0 .38rem 1rem !important; } .about-page h3 + ul li::before, .about-page .about-contacts li::before{ top:.85rem; } }
/* === Ê®ôÈ°åÁâπÊïàÔºöÂ∑¶ÂÅ¥Á¥ÖÁ∑ö + Â∫ïÈÉ®Á≤âËâ≤Áü≠Á∑ö === / .about-page h3{ background:none!important; border-radius:0!important; position:relative; } .about-page h3::before{ width:3px!important; / ‰øùÊåÅÂ∑¶ÂÅ¥ÂØ¶ÂøÉÁ¥ÖÁ∑ö */ } .about-page h3::after{ content:&quot;&quot;; position:absolute; left:.75rem; bottom:-2px; width:64px; height:2px; background:var(&ndash;about-accent); border-radius:2px; opacity:.82; }
/* === Hero ÂÖßÂèØÈªûÊìäÈÄ£ÁµêÂ∞àÂ±¨Ê®£ÂºèÔºàËàá‰∏ÄËà¨ strong ÂçÄÂàÜÔºâ === / / ËÆäÊõ¥Ôºö‰ΩøÁî®ËºÉÈ°ØÁúºÁöÑËóçËâ≤Á≥ªÔºåËàá‰∏ÄËà¨Á≤âËâ≤ accent ÂÅöÂçÄÈöî / .about-page .about-hero a{ &ndash;hero-link-accent:#1d6fff; position:relative; display:inline-block; padding:.16rem .55rem .20rem; margin:.08rem .18rem .08rem 0; color:#0b3d91; / Ê∑±ËóçÊñáÂ≠ó / background:rgba(29,111,255,.08); / Ê∑°ËóçÂ∫ï */ border-radius:9px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; line-height:1.18; vertical-align:baseline; border:1px solid rgba(29,111,255,.20); transition:background .22s,color .22s,box-shadow .22s,border-color .22s,transform .08s; } body.dark .about-page .about-hero a{ color:#9fd1ff; background:rgba(29,111,255,.12); border-color:rgba(29,111,255,.28); } .about-page .about-hero a:hover, .about-page .about-hero a:focus-visible{ background:var(&ndash;hero-link-accent); color:#fff; border-color:var(&ndash;hero-link-accent); box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(29,111,255,.12); text-decoration:none; transform:translateY(-1px); } body.dark .about-page .about-hero a:hover, body.dark .about-page .about-hero a:focus-visible{ box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(29,111,255,.18); } .about-page .about-hero a:active{ transform:translateY(0); }
/* ÈÄ£ÁµêÂÖßÁöÑ strong ÂéªÈô§ÂéüÈ´ò‰∫ÆÔºåÂÉÖÁπºÊâøÈ°èËâ≤ */ .about-page .about-hero a strong{ background:none!important; padding:0!important; margin:0!important; border-radius:0!important; color:inherit!important; line-height:inherit!important; }
/* Ë°åÂãïÁâàÂæÆË™øÈñìË∑ù */ @media (max-width:640px){ .about-page .about-hero a{padding:.14rem .5rem .18rem;margin:.06rem .15rem .06rem 0;} }
/* === ÈáçÊßãÂØµÁâ© TooltipÔºàÁî± ::after ÊîπÊàêÂÖßÂµåÂÖÉÁ¥† .pet-tipÔºâ === / .about-page .pet-info{ position:relative; cursor:help; display:inline-block; line-height:1; } .about-page .pet-info &gt; strong{ / ÂêçÁ®± pill Ê®£ÂºèÔºàËàá hero ÈÄ£Áµê‰∏ÄËá¥È¢®Ê†ºËóçËâ≤Á≥ªÔºâ */ &ndash;pet-pill:#1d6fff; display:inline-block; background:rgba(29,111,255,.10); color:#0b3d91; padding:.28rem .65rem .34rem; margin:.08rem .28rem .08rem 0; font-weight:600; font-size:.78rem; line-height:1.05; border:1px solid rgba(29,111,255,.28); border-radius:11px; text-decoration:none; transition:background .22s,color .22s,border-color .22s,box-shadow .22s,transform .18s; } body.dark .about-page .pet-info &gt; strong{ background:rgba(29,111,255,.18); color:#9fd1ff; border-color:rgba(29,111,255,.38); } .about-page .pet-info:hover &gt; strong, .about-page .pet-info:focus-visible &gt; strong, .about-page .pet-info.tip-open &gt; strong{ background:var(&ndash;pet-pill); color:#fff; border-color:var(&ndash;pet-pill); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(29,111,255,.20); transform:translateY(-2px); } body.dark .about-page .pet-info:hover &gt; strong, body.dark .about-page .pet-info:focus-visible &gt; strong, body.dark .about-page .pet-info.tip-open &gt; strong{ box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(29,111,255,.28); }
.about-page .pet-info .pet-tip{ position:absolute; left:50%; top:100%; transform:translate(-50%,10px) scale(.94); transform-origin:top center; background:#fff; color:#222; border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12); border-radius:12px; padding:.65rem .75rem .7rem; min-width:180px; max-width:240px; width:max-content; font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.35; letter-spacing:.35px; box-shadow:0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,.35); opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transition:opacity .22s,transform .22s; backdrop-filter:blur(8px); text-align:left; z-index:30; white-space:normal; } body.dark .about-page .pet-info .pet-tip{ background:rgba(38,38,42,.92); color:#eee; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.18); box-shadow:0 12px 34px -12px rgba(0,0,0,.65); }
